{"tid":327352,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《學界電競》聯校電競大賽 學生爭做「學界」一哥","createTime":"2017-07-18T16:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T18:38:23.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbe005225f2eb922585cbdf19fac4f0be3211ca","tid":327352,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-01-fi_324341009596c93d4274ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-01-fi_324341009596c93d4274ba.jpg&h=b92b877f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n電子競技（e-Sports）的名號在過去幾個月浮現大眾耳邊，隨著政府開始委託數碼港研究電競行業前景之際，「香港電競」有望開始追上世界進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。在剛過去的星期六，由成立4年的香港學生電子競技總會（HKFSES）主辦的第二屆《聯校電子競技大賽》於數碼港場地舉行，經過過百個隊伍進行淘汰賽後，最後由8個學校代表隊爭奪 學界 王者寶座。HKFSES主席梁雅姿（Gabriella）寄望會有更多人材投身電競行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，亦想藉是次比賽令學校及學生家長更了解電子競技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nmplus.hk/game/%E3%80%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E3%80%8B%E8%81%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fgame%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B3%25BD%2F&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9c8449f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmplus.hk/game/%E3%80%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E3%80%8B%E8%81%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD/</a></div>"},{"pid":"eef2c38fd25b0d811994e22a1503fcf5f584df36","tid":327352,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">8個學校代表隊 爭奪「學界」王者之名</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n是次比賽經由過百隊隊伍進行數輪預賽，終於上星期六由以下八個學校代表隊伍成功進級八強，一同爭奪「學界」冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-06_444993783596c88746eae9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-06_444993783596c88746eae9.jpg&h=5a454c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">8個學校代表隊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-03_1470943646596c887bc91ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-03_1470943646596c887bc91ea.jpg&h=0277d82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當時人頭湧湧，不乏同學們的支持者。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-07_880159946596c8fec1c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-07_880159946596c8fec1c736.jpg&h=ea0b4e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">同學們都凝神貫注地進行比賽。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-07_880159946596c8fec1c736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-07_880159946596c8fec1c736.jpg&h=ea0b4e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">台上一分鐘，台下十年功。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-08_318158153596c91f5f2c90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-08_318158153596c91f5f2c90.jpg&h=17cb99f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">各隊比賽氣氛濃厚，時不時出現大叫場面。</span></div>"},{"pid":"2045cb398190c6de68cf0237c4ceea8b57813333","tid":327352,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"又LOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df48e99241149674238c4d23bde80055b430553","tid":327352,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a25b73ecad047b1867f906a79dc42aa6e044c1","tid":327352,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又LOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係都world of tank 啦"},{"pid":"43f87c30b282f88711036534c94aeb6f5ce43563","tid":327352,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">學生總會主席指家長成阻力 但持樂觀態度發展「學界電競」</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\nHKFSES 主席梁雅姿（Gabriella）坦言，學校非最大壓力來源，而是有部分家長擔心子女會因比賽賽程或是練習影響學業。其實要改變社會風氣不易，一來大部分香港傳統家庭教育不鼓勵子女發展自我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，尤其當香港的固有教育模式及一直不變，令學子無法發掘自身興趣或長處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，長遠對香港電競發展存隱憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過Gabriella對「學界電競」發展持樂觀態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原因是本年度比賽的規模比起上年度大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，學校支持度亦相對上年來得高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，小編期望「學界電競」在未來能發展至全港中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，到時香港整體實力及人才培養便會漸上軌道。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/-2017-07-17-5.56.53_1884648695596c89d7bd432-1024x572.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F-2017-07-17-5.56.53_1884648695596c89d7bd432-1024x572.png&h=03be1ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「Gab姐」坦言，學校非最大阻力，反而壓力來源自學生家長的不了解。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n同時，比賽營運人手亦十分短缺，記者在場內觀察，工作人員比起選手及觀眾真的來得少，更有部分工作人員身兼數職，時不時東奔西跑。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-05_1287922581596c8881b15d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-05_1287922581596c8881b15d3.jpg&h=db1543b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">場外設置試玩區，但鮮有工作人員介紹玩法。</span></div><br />\n<br />\nGabriella期望未來會有更多人手投身電競行業，她解釋道，其實電子競技不只得選手，營運一次比賽所需的人手，與其他大型活動如足球比賽無異，所需的人手包括如導播、場地管理、技術支援、推廣（廣告、平面設計）&hellip;&hellip;等，各單位缺一不可。梁雅姿表示，同學們想投身電競行業可以向這類方向發展，其實並非只能以選手為目標。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-02_1828630945596c887aa077e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-02_1828630945596c887aa077e.jpg&h=260924fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現場邀請了幾位資深主播評述比賽。（圖左為主播－ICE，圖右為主播－Sang）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/es-01_1287361774596c88797dc30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fes-01_1287361774596c88797dc30.jpg&h=786076a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">是次比賽的規格不輸正規電競比賽。</span></div>"},{"pid":"dd29b1aa5076030b0b8848246e460fe9ca94c38e","tid":327352,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:21:22.000Z","msg":"咁都不輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3621c40ad2dd6acc231df85207372eb8e6703e","tid":327352,"uid":40938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又LOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學雞唔玩lol 仲識玩啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8f2a19eaff03408fb5c093ba0413700b59ee3f","tid":327352,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"條女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531d16a4c6b9a83630232cfc234042c343557dce","tid":327352,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c572924a215ee34b7424c955f53ff13937f990fb","tid":327352,"uid":52590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電咩競啊<br />\n<br />\n根本就係聯校LOL大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}